*kmail-3.5.0 (22 Nov 2005)

  22 Nov 2005; Dan Armak <danarmak@gentoo.org> +kmail-3.5.0.ebuild:
  Ebuilds for KDE 3.5.0 final. It is not yet released, and is package.masked.

